  "body": "\r\n## Problem \r\nSuggestions/issues on implementation in Figma are [here](https://www.figma.com/file/Tf5nfkYvpbnNCo4rKLK7lS/Feedback-for-Mobile?node-id=1902-133425&t=h8BhUXUBEHnWas6r-4)\r\n\r\n\r\n## Expected fixes\r\n\r\n### Slideshow > Slideshow\r\n- [ ] Fix/update illustration, should not be cropped on top\r\n- [ ] Add swiping - user should be able to swipe between the slideshow and navigate\r\n- [ ] \"You're already use Status\" - change font size - should be in regular, not medium\r\n- [ ] \"By continuing\"\r\n     - \"By continuing...\" text should be in regular, not in medium.\r\n     - Terms of Use is the only part that should be in medium\r\n     - Also force to two lines like in design\r\n- [ ] Change  color, opacity and blur of the drawers - doesn't match design\r\n- [ ]  Change button size, should be 32x32 version\r\n\r\n### Slideshow > Sign In-Transition\r\n- [ ] The background illustration should be the slideshow illustration, not an additional one (full comment [here](https://www.figma.com/file/Tf5nfkYvpbnNCo4rKLK7lS?node-id=1902:133425#427905184))\r\n\r\n### Slideshow > Transition\r\n- [ ] Change transition to the bttom > top (full comment [here](https://www.figma.com/file/Tf5nfkYvpbnNCo4rKLK7lS?node-id=1902:133425#427916978))\r\n",
